OL,6,FIn a statement to Sky News on Monday
OL,7,FMr Staunton doubled down on his
OL,8,Fposition, insisting "I think it is
OL,9,Fpretty obvious to everyone what was
OL,10,Freally going on".
OL,12,FMr Staunton said: "It was in the
OL,13,Finterests of the business as well as
OL,14,Fbeing fair for the postmasters that
OL,15,Fthere was faster progress on
OL,16,Fexoneration and that compensation was
OL,17,Fmore generous, but we didn't see any
OL,18,Freal movement until after the Mr Bates
OL,19,Fprogramme."
