OL,6,FMore than 10.3 million people have
OL,7,Fwatched the final episode of the
OL,8,Fseries making it one of the .
OL,10,FIn 1999 the Post Office introduced
OL,11,Fdigital accounting software named
OL,12,FHorizon - created by Japanese tech
OL,13,Ffirm Fujitsu - which replaced the
OL,14,Fpaper-based process of the past.
OL,16,FBut it soon became clear to some sub-
OL,17,Fpostmasters that the software was
OL,18,Fcreating discrepancies in their
OL,19,Faccounts, making it look like cash was
OL,20,Fmissing.
