OL,4,Cclaims ex-Post Office boss lied
OL,6,FA sub-postmaster is someone not
OL,7,Fdirectly employed by the Post Office,
OL,8,Fwho runs a separate retail business
OL,9,Fwhich hosts a Post Office facility on
OL,10,Ftheir site.
OL,12,FThe idea is that an in-house Post
OL,13,FOffice would drive customers to their
OL,14,Fbusiness.
OL,16,FBut many didn't - and the Post Office,
OL,17,Fwhich has the power to run private
OL,18,Fprosecutions, sought to have many sub-
OL,19,Fpostmasters convicted of fraud and
OL,20,Ftheft.
