OL,6,FWatch the trailer for ITV's Mr Bates
OL,7,Fvs The Post Office
OL,9,FBetween 1999 and 2015, 736 sub-
OL,10,Fpostmasters were wrongfully convicted
OL,11,Fbut concerns with the faulty Horizon
OL,12,Fsystem were raised in court as early
OL,13,Fas 2003.
OL,15,FBy 2012, potential problems with
OL,16,FHorizon were so apparent the Post
OL,17,FOffice launched a review to satisfy
OL,18,Fpoliticians who had been complaining
OL,19,Fon behalf of their aggrieved
OL,20,Fconstituents.
