OL,6,FThe Post Office however continued
OL,7,Fprosecuting sub-postmasters until 2015
OL,8,Fbut the miscarriage of justice was
OL,9,Fonly confirmed in 2019 when the High
OL,10,FCourt ruled that Horizon was to blame.
OL,12,FA number of compensation schemes were
OL,13,Fintroduced by the government and #87
OL,14,Fmillion was eventually paid out
OL,15,Fthrough the Horizon Shortfall Scheme
OL,16,Fto more than 2,500 sub-postmasters who
OL,17,Flost money but weren't convicted.
